text: Albin Lundin (born March 15, 1996) is a Swedish professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Timrå IK of the HockeyAllsvenskan (Allsv). Lundin made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Djurgårdens IF Hockey during the 2014–15 SHL season.https://www.difhockey.se/artikel/5563/ He has also played for Skellefteå AIK. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Almtuna IS players Category:Djurgårdens IF Hockey players Category:Skellefteå AIK players Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards
